text: Sobeknakht was high steward during the 12th Dynasty in ancient Egypt. Sobeknakht (Sbk-nḫt, "Sobek is strong") may also refer to: *Sobeknakht I, official and nomarch during the Second Intermediate Period, father of the one below *Sobeknakht II, official and nomarch during the Second Intermediate Period, son of Sobeknakht I *Sobeknakht (king's daughter), princess during the late 12th or early 13th Dynasty Category:Theophoric names
title: Sobeknakht (disambiguation)
